            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le long d'un ciel crépusculâtre,\nUne cloche angéluse en paix\nL'air exilescent et marâtre\nQui ne pardonnera jamais."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 2,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 5,
                    "line_text": "Paissant des débris de vaisselle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 6,
                    "line_text": "Là-bas, au talus des remparts,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 7,
                    "line_text": "Se profile une haridelle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 8,
                    "line_text": "Convalescente ; il se fait tard.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Paissant des débris de vaisselle,\nLà-bas, au talus des remparts,\nSe profile une haridelle\nConvalescente ; il se fait tard."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 9,
                    "line_text": "Qui m'aima jamais ? Je m'entête",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 10,
                    "line_text": "Sur ce refrain bien impuissant,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 11,
                    "line_text": "Sans songer que je suis bien bête",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 12,
                    "line_text": "De me faire du mauvais sang.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Qui m'aima jamais ? Je m'entête\nSur ce refrain bien impuissant,\nSans songer que je suis bien bête\nDe me faire du mauvais sang."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 13,
                    "line_text": "Je possède un propre physique,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 14,
                    "line_text": "Un cœur d'enfant bien élevé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Et pour un cerveau magnifique",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Le mien n'est pas mal, vous savez.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Je possède un propre physique,\nUn cœur d'enfant bien élevé,\nEt pour un cerveau magnifique\nLe mien n'est pas mal, vous savez."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Eh bien, ayant pleuré l'Histoire,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "J'ai voulu vivre un brin heureux ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "C'était trop demander, faut croire ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "J'avais l'air de parler hébreux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh bien, ayant pleuré l'Histoire,\nJ'ai voulu vivre un brin heureux ;\nC'était trop demander, faut croire ;\nJ'avais l'air de parler hébreux."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ah ! Tiens, mon cœur, de grâce, laisse",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 22,
                    "line_text": "Lorsque j'y songe, en vérité,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "J'en ai des sueurs de faiblesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "À choir dans la malpropreté.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ah ! Tiens, mon cœur, de grâce, laisse\nLorsque j'y songe, en vérité,\nJ'en ai des sueurs de faiblesse,\nÀ choir dans la malpropreté."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 7,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Le cœur me piaffe de génie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+4",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "Éperdument pourtant, mon Dieu !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Et si quelqu'une veut ma vie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Moi je ne demande pas mieux !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Le cœur me piaffe de génie\nÉperdument pourtant, mon Dieu !\nEt si quelqu'une veut ma vie,\nMoi je ne demande pas mieux !"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 8,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Eh va, pauvre âme véhémente !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Plonge, être, en leurs Jourdains blasés,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Deux frictions de vie courante",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "T'auront bien vite exorcisé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Eh va, pauvre âme véhémente !\nPlonge, être, en leurs Jourdains blasés,\nDeux frictions de vie courante\nT'auront bien vite exorcisé."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 9,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Hélas, qui peut m'en répondre !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Tenez, peut-être savez-vous",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Ce que c'est qu'une âme hypocondre ?",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Hélas, qui peut m'en répondre !\nTenez, peut-être savez-vous\nCe que c'est qu'une âme hypocondre ?"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 10,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Ô Hélène, j'erre en ma chambre ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Et tandis que tu prends le thé,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Là-bas dans l'or d'un fier septembre,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "Je frissonne de tous mes membres,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Ô Hélène, j'erre en ma chambre ;\nEt tandis que tu prends le thé,\nLà-bas dans l'or d'un fier septembre,\nJe frissonne de tous mes membres,"
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 11,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "En m'inquiétant de ta santé.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "5+4",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                }
